<normalizedToken id="AA692F6341DD1513B17592D8782B95C8" originalValue="Paraíba">Paraiba</normalizedToken>
- Universidade Estadual da 
<normalizedToken id="FBC27FC3C35288C1A8B2A94C6F9F2DB6" originalValue="Paraíba”">Paraiba&quot;</normalizedToken>
(CRFS/UEPB), #2766. 
<normalizedToken id="55ED30926FEB68FF83DF2C790A397BF1" originalValue="Várzea">Varzea</normalizedToken>
do Lopes, Itabirito, MG, Brazil. Cave VL29/30. 02-06/x/2011. Leg. Speleology team of Carste consultants.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C642BC5F4165E7BC319B8B09E62F97D7" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
